          .col-md-6.text-center.mt-5.mb-2
            h3.browsing-headline  Browse by shape:
            ul.browsing-ul
              li
                a(href="/products?filter=1&page=0&shape1=Twin") Twin
              li
                a(href="/products?filter=1&page=0&shape0=Directional") Directional

  .parallax-3